text: Yelyzaveta Mereshko (born 8 July 1992) is a Ukrainian Paralympic swimmer. In 2015, she set the world record for the S6 100 metres freestyle event. She won four gold medals and a bronze medal at the 2016 Summer Paralympics. == References == Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Paralympic gold medalists for Ukraine Category:Ukrainian swimmers Category:Paralympic bronze medalists for Ukraine Category:Sportspeople with disabilities, type S6
